annotations.description: Nog Season Is Finally Here! Every year I rejoice in making one of my favorite drinks EGG NOG!!!!! And this year we will be doing quite a few of them so strap...
annotations.title: A Presidential History Lesson with General Harrison's Egg Nog

textContent:
1.5oz (45ml) Applejack
.5oz (15ml) Demerara Syrup
2 Dashes Angostura Bitters
1 Whole Egg
Top Dry (Hard) Cider (Of Your Choice)
Grated Nutmeg Garnish

Shake all but cider with ice. 
Strain into small rocks glass. 
Top with cider.

title: General Harisson's Egg Nog
